com.hpe.caf.worker.document.model

Interface Subdocument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Document, DocumentWorkerObject

    public interface Subdocument
extends Document
    Represents a direct or indirect subdocument of the document being processed.

    Subdocuments are documents in their own right and can also have fields, failures, and subdocuments of their own.

      • delete

        void delete()
        Deletes this subdocument.

        After a subdocument has been deleted the Document.reset() method may still be used to restore it to its original state, but other methods which would query or manipulate the deleted document should not be called. Calling these methods will result in undefined behavior.
